# 1. Scale Definitions

| Scale | Meaning |
|-------|---------|
| Micro | Decisions, moments, signals, thoughts |
| Meso | Projects, missions, arcs |
| Macro | Markets, cultures, civilizations |
| Meta | Archetypes, invariants, mythic structures |

