# 3. Interpretation

The same **12 functions** operate at **4 depths**, giving:

$$12 \times 4 = 48 \text{ fractal roles}$$

And every one of those 48 roles inherits the same invariants:
* 0.7 ethics
* ZPC
* Narrative Delta
* Bombadil zero
* Time Trident

**This is why PantheonOS is scale invariant.**

